== 制作 ==
[[张艺谋|张艺谋]]执导的电影版《[[山楂树之恋_(电影)|山楂树之恋]]》曾取得巨大成功。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2012-03-30/06583593947.shtml |title=《山楂树之恋》首播告捷 李路对王珞丹表演满意 |date=2012-03-30 |accessdate=2014-04-04 |work=新浪 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407081247/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2012-03-30/06583593947.shtml |dead-url=no}}</ref>

该剧情节细腻、动人，讲述特殊政治大环境时代的被摧残的爱情，引发关注，观众表示“可以接受”，也间接启发人们，任何人都无法摆脱政治环境的约束和控制。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/photoview/00AJ0003/62497.html |title=王珞丹《山楂树之恋》催泪剧照 |accessdate=2014-04-04|date=2012-03-26 |work=网易 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407090117/http://ent.163.com/photoview/00AJ0003/62497.html |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2012-03-22/14423587546.shtml |title=《山楂树之恋》催泪袭来 王珞丹变身哭戏王(图) |accessdate=2014-04-04| date=2012-03-22 |work=新浪 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407081303/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2012-03-22/14423587546.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/12/0318/07/7SS3VU2700032DGD.html |title=《山楂树之恋》热播 王珞丹:母亲劝我别演了 |accessdate=2014-04-04| date=2012-03-18 |work=网易 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305023656/http://ent.163.com/12/0318/07/7SS3VU2700032DGD.html |archive-date=2016-03-05 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>

王珞丹表示出于“静秋”是“无怨无悔”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2012-03-15/09273580939.shtml |title=王珞丹谈《山楂树之恋》：演静秋无怨无悔(图) |accessdate=2014-04-04|date=2012-03-15 |work=新浪 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407081253/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2012-03-15/09273580939.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

